57 service and excellence; now therefore,
58 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE
59 LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, That Ms. Clarene Teague-Johnson will
60 be highly honored on an unforgettable afternoon filled with
61 inspiration, celebration, and community, and we endeavor to
62 continue uplifting and investing in those who make a
63 difference, both today and tomorrow.
